.Dd May 24, 2006
.Dt GETMAXPARTITIONS 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm getmaxpartitions
.Nd get the maximum number of partitions allowed per disk
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb libutil
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In util.h
.Ft int
.Fn getmaxpartitions void
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Fn getmaxpartitions
returns the number of partitions that are allowed per disk on the
system, or \-1 in case of an error, setting the global
.Va errno
variable.
The possible values for
.Va errno
are the same as in
.Xr sysctl 3 .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr getrawpartition 3 ,
.Xr sysctl 3
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
function call appeared in
.Nx 1.2 .
